AIG to Sue ICP Asset Management, Moore Capital, N.Y. Times Says

-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 
2011-04-28T04:39:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/aig-to-sue-icp-asset-management-moore-capital-n-y-times-says.html
American International Group plans
to file suit today against ICP Asset Management and  Moore
Capital  for alleged losses on mortgage securities insured by the
company, the New York Times reported, citing a copy of the suit
obtained by the newspaper.  The suit may be the first of several aimed a recovering
billions of dollars in losses from what AIG designated as
“fraudulent conduct” by companies it dealt with, the newspaper
said.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
